<sect1 id="dir_38cb15a289b9cc4a3f53b331ae426885_1autotoc_md349">
<title>helios::engine::modules::physics</title><para>Physics simulation and collision detection subsystem for the game engine.</para>
<para>This namespace provides the complete physics layer for the helios game engine, including movement simulation, collision detection, and physics-related event handling.</para>
</sect1>
